Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.50,0:00:04.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.50,0:00:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在林檎转学到田茂农之后不久
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.97,0:00:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~　等一下　小老板
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛　不用那么急的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.61,0:00:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邂逅总是那么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.54,0:00:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现也总是那么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.06,0:00:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们每到这时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像穷途末路一样不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:25.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这　这是咋的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.55,0:02:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过分啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.27,0:02:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报警了没
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.73,0:02:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连围栏也木有的啥都木有的田地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.64,0:02:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁　有目击者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要线索
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对　就是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.27,0:02:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿着灰色的外套
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.98,0:02:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱着蔬菜跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那　那是在大概几点左右
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天照顾完牛之后准备回去的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.01,0:02:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概晚上8点多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.95,0:02:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候这个掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是事实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.76,0:02:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算怎么办　过真鸟继
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:03:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子的话　就必须严查事实和动机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂且不说是偷吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可如果是饿的不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.13,0:03:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕特拉什　我累挺了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.84,0:03:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　节子　花子　卖火柴的小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸福王子的燕子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世上总是牺牲那些纯洁弱小的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.35,0:03:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.58,0:03:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？中泽农
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正和过真鸟继讨论有可能阻碍社会发展的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.69,0:03:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个　不是猴子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猴子？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂　耕作　像猴子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　是的　像猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等　那可是用两脚走路的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野生的猴子也可以在短时间内用两脚走路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.29,0:03:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱着西瓜跑之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你　你有见过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和农住的地方是偏远农村
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.38,0:03:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗和猴子还有山鸡都会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本传说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　太好啦　没有不幸的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.49,0:03:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的　解散　解散
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是　战争才刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么第一次应对猿猴出现很头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对策考虑会议开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么一个人一个人的发表建议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的　那么我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们老家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田地周围都有通电栅栏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通电？噼里啪啦的那种？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不至于会死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快实行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.27,0:04:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为意见确实是没什么错误
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,O
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给他吃的不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是肚子饿了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.11,0:05:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给他吃的肚子不饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不会来破坏农田
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好　赶快实行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不是个坏主意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.33,0:05:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但问题是受袭击的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.45,0:05:25.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是果树啊田地而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明确的说有半分开玩笑的性质
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不认为会因为肚子不饿了就老实了的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继好像很了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.51,0:05:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鄙人　畑耕作　16岁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.85,0:05:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其大半的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都投入了和猿猴的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个就是超级仁君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是之前仁君的30倍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能一次发射30枚火箭烟火
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来很拽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:06:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让猴子们尝尝留下心理阴影级别的冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦　好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火药上潮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好　好孩子绝不要去瞄发射口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行　绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些俗人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来告诉你们我的秘籍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么秘籍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了　你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿猴和人类都是灵长类动物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿出诚意来对话的话一定能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驳回
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猎人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庆幸只有一支猿猴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它处理掉就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,处理掉？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死它貌似不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,农业是无情的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经做好了这个觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道一个厉害的猎人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好　我叫大森
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊？这个奇怪的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂　说的太直接了　林檎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.09,0:07:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊这个奇怪的大叔是咋回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.85,0:07:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧你这大胸都说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事啊过真鸟继
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:51.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说交给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有些许小期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找这个宅男样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人都是九分看外貌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一分是例外
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.84,0:08:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就等着吃惊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看大森先生这幅样子可是吹箭的高手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吹箭的高手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下是大森流吹箭术的开山祖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来　吹箭在什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.05,0:08:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.32,0:08:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是吹箭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是狙击吹箭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狙击吹箭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.81,0:08:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一看还以为是漫画的海报什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来完全误解了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:39.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不　这就是漫画的海报
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是把漫画的海报卷起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做成的吹箭筒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大森先生您平时用这吹箭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都狩猎什么样的猎物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一些现充吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉　原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:09:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个　抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.40,0:09:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大森先生你是做什么工作的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无业
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被在下调制的强力麻药射中的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是什么猴子都会立马　升天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,商品名也是秘密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.64,0:09:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是将竹轮贴在嘴唇上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以命名为「乳头式架势」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那个是被叫做现充杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不想听
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死猴子　把你剥个精光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.04,0:10:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄了它弄了它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:10.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这猴子　手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耕作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的　林檎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以同情他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.71,0:10:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是　首先是要保护田地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道是因为受伤才脱离队伍的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.39,0:10:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是脱离队伍后才受伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之就是多余的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是快点想想怎么处理这家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:48.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,良田　现在不是说笑的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是蠢　过真鸟继
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经考虑过这猴子的出路了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和动物园工作的熟人商量过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问他是否愿意接收这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此　动物园
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的　正好现在养的都是母猴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这只雄性放进去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为金龟婿也能促进那边的气氛活跃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的人生　不　新的猴生要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉　良田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住你的恩惠了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说喵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住恩惠喵的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我　我才不是为了得到你的表扬喵的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.59,0:11:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是　是为了猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.85,0:11:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了　咋的啦　耕作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有重要的事想跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　嗯嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以等我一个小时吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:12:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想尽早说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋　我有很多必须要准备的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.44,0:12:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.99,0:12:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我进来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎欢迎　耕太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你房间布局换了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是的　你不要紧张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要洗澡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶　不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说　全部结束后一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　是继
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.33,0:12:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　我叫他来的　进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我进来　哇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她把室内布局换了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白瞎了这么可爱的YES图案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耕太　你有什么事情要说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　嗯　是关于林檎的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:12:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:12:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥啊　我还什么都没说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.08,0:13:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正就是去死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我活得好好的呢　话说　你抽什么风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙　作死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么　作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之　你们来看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友们　来　一起唱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是草壁由佳的DVD吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都扔了那么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你还藏着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:25.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是用零花钱重新买的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说　你们看由佳炭　没注意到什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　虽然是废话　人看起来很亲切随和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都不会想到她和那个木下居然是同一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢　脸上一直是挂着笑容的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个　笑容啊　笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.69,0:13:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那姑娘来到这以后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.23,0:13:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次都没笑过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚进教室的时候　内裤事件的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饭的时候　玩国王游戏的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和农比赛坚持到最后的时候　猴子得救的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:13:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,林檎一直都是绷着脸的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.62,0:14:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为　这个笑容是职业微笑罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然如此　不过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起生活的同伴一点都没有笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.17,0:14:09.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会觉得寂寞么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　的确如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起逗笑　缺少我的出场是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你在这里　木下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说　你不想看看我的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶　好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,dark　matter
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此　只能硬碰硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木下同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.48,0:14:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,农这家伙　太让人羡慕嫉妒恨了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过　干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:15:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何呀　我的技术不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的看我的看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此　这招如何　是这边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那　那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.69,0:15:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的“沈体”出卖了你　不用“面强”的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就把一切交给“蒯感”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.05,0:15:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经到极限了吗　不行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在　该我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我其实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你总是绷着脸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:16:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我以为你在这过得不开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.70,0:16:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以　你想逗我发笑是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起　我没有恶意　那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶搞的分寸没掌握好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我笑不出的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始别人说我表情有点僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为是有些累了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.83,0:16:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就没想太多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是　渐渐的　无论怎么努力　都笑不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的表情也都摆不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自然就不能在原来的地方再待下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.85,0:16:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像那个猴子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是　那个猴子找到了自己的归宿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以　你也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:17:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你　对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界上真有笑不出来这回事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然说不准　但是应该是精神上的问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.15,0:17:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草壁由佳　木下林檎　是不是疲于应付
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周围人的期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此　休息下会恢复吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都不好说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想逗她笑　想逗她笑这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是我们的一厢情愿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耕作　耕作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若旦那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是若旦那　我是盖娅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盖娅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对　我是来向你传达信息的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.45,0:18:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信　信息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.83,0:18:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起来吧　耕作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们人类　对我都做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而现在　你是在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.86,0:18:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘记　耕作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盖娅我会一直向你耕作着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倾诉着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等　等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.33,0:18:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盖娅　盖娅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.03,0:18:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类到底对盖娅做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.80,0:19:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想带林檎去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.81,0:19:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让她看看那片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实　那片土地和现在的木下有相似之处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到那个　木下同学也会有所感悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.64,0:19:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在农校里有农业俱乐部　也就是农俱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们现在要去的是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从前辈那里继承的项目所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,项目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.36,0:19:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对　希望你也能加入进来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:19:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不先看番茄地么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.02,0:20:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先看这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸摸那泥土
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泥土
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.03,0:20:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又硬又干
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　那是死掉的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.69,0:20:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里种不了庄稼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以是死掉了的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.40,0:20:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连作破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,补习的时候学过了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在同一个地方持续种植一种作物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会导致无法耕种
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有些肤浅的人　通过使用化肥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算来避免产量下降
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.63,0:20:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果导致病虫害的扩散　农药过度使用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.36,0:20:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是愚蠢的恶性循环的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.70,0:21:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这土地不能恢复到原样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.36,0:21:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这块田以前和刚才看到的土地是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.22,0:21:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本是同一块田地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.89,0:21:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈们在农俱中开始这个项目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们继承下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能恢复到这个程度已经花了七年时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七年
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.87,0:21:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然　还没有完全恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.20,0:21:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是　作物在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.84,0:21:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力地生长着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.54,0:21:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那　这里会重生是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耕作　我想尝尝那个番茄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.27,0:22:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶　现在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.20,0:22:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想尝一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.52,0:22:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.81,0:22:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为还没熟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.14,0:22:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.45,0:22:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.70,0:22:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.21,0:22:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.09,0:22:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.66,0:23:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,林檎　你刚刚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.09,0:23:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.75,0:23:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木下同学　也尝尝这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.17,0:23:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个更红
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.50,0:23:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　木下同学　吃这个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.54,0:23:14.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个已经很红了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.31,0:23:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.61,0:23:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用心耕种的作物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.09,0:23:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以充盈人的身心　让人感到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.28,0:23:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,培育作物是最快乐的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.74,0:23:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望有一天你也能体会到这份喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
